// ----------------------------------------------------------------
// Mood
// ----------------------------------------------------------------

Table: mood
bleak and oppressive — hope feels like a luxury
tense and paranoid — trust no one
eerie and unsettling — something watches from the shadows
grim but determined — survival demands sacrifice
mysterious and dreamlike — reality feels thin here
desperate and urgent — every hour counts
melancholy and haunted — the past refuses to die
dangerous and chaotic — alliances shift without warning
claustrophobic and suffocating — there is no safe direction to run
grimly comedic — even the corpses seem annoyed at the situation
epic and monumental — every choice carries the weight of history
cold and clinical — whatever is happening here was planned in detail

